零點二五毫克或血液中酒精濃度\r\n　　達百分之零點零五以上。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/ULDM/110%2c%e5%85%ad%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c32%2c20210303%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"ULDM,110,六交簡,32,20210303,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"六交簡","JNO":"32","JDATE":"20210303","JTITLE":"公共危險"}